  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_1' aria-label=\" Gajanan Dattatray Gore versus The State of Maharashtra & Anr. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('1','2025','2025_7_1980_1997','2025INSC913'); ><font size='4'> <strong>GAJANAN DATTATRAY GORE<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>THE STATE OF MAHARASHTRA & ANR. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 7 S.C.R. 1980</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 913</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010008262025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : J.B. PARDIWALA<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, R MAHADEVAN</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Whether the bail granted to the appellant-accused on the basis of his undertaking to deposit Rs.25,00,000/- was rightly cancelled by the High Court on his failure to deposit the same. Headnotes&dagger; Directions by Supreme Court &ndash; Bail &ndash; Grant of, on the basis accused &ndash; Practice deprecated &ndash; Directions issued: Held: High Courts as well as the Trial Courts shall decide the plea for regular bail or anticipatory bail strictly on the merits of the case and shall not exercise their discretion in this regard on any undertaking or any statement<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 28-07-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CRIMINAL APPEAL No. 3219/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Dismissed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('1','2025','2025_7_1980_1997','2025INSC913','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('1','2025','2025_7_1980_1997','2025INSC913','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('1','2025','2025_7_1980_1997','2025INSC913');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('1','2025','2025_7_1980_1997','2025INSC913','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
